<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Whitehorn</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Nestled in a tranquil location in the heart of the North East Calgary, the Whitehorn residential community is one of the most desirable neighborhoods in the entire city. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Given its close proximity to a myriad of leisure and shopping facilities, the <span class="par-xl">Whitehorn Real estate offers its residents an unlimited choice of activities to keep themselves engaged in</span>. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">The Whitehorn Community Association is instrumental in regularly organizing youth dances, craft fairs and karate classes for the benefit of the kids and their parents residing in the community. </p>
        </div>
